Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.69,AnneHappy_Main,HIBARI,0,0,0,,Tớ đã bảo rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.71,AnneHappy_Top,HIBARI,0,0,0,,Mực... Mực...
