Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.44,AnneHappy_Main,HANAKO,0,0,0,,A, Ren-chan nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.61,AnneHappy_Main,HIBIKI,0,0,0,,Đừng có tự ý gọi cậu ấy là "Ren-chan".
